    "Recommended for You": "Inapendekezwa Kwako",
    "A peaceful retreat for couples or solo travelers. Featuring a cozy double bed, en-suite hot shower, air conditioning, complimentary Wi-Fi, and a hearty breakfast every morning — everything you need after a thrilling day on safari.": "Mahali pa amani kwa wanandoa au wasafiri peke yao. Ina kitanda kizuri cha double, bafu ya ndani yenye maji ya moto, kiyoyozi, Wi-Fi bila malipo, na kiamsha kinywa kizuri kila asubuhi — kila unachohitaji baada ya siku ya kusisimua ya safari.",
    "Thoughtfully designed for groups of three, this spacious room combines one double bed and one single bed. Enjoy the same premium comfort — A/C, Wi-Fi, hot shower, and breakfast — with room for everyone to unwind.": "Kimebuniwa kwa makini kwa ajili ya watu watatu. Chumba hiki kikubwa kina kitanda kimoja cha double na cha single. Furahia starehe zilezile za hali ya juu — kiyoyozi, Wi-Fi, bafu ya maji moto, na kiamsha kinywa — na nafasi ya kutosha kwa kila mtu kupumzika.",
    "Our most generous room, built for families of up to four. Two full double beds, a spacious ~45 m² layout, and all the comforts of home. The perfect base for families exploring the Serengeti, Ngorongoro, and Lake Manyara.": "Chumba chetu kikubwa zaidi, kimejengwa kwa ajili ya familia za watu wanne. Vitanda viwili vya double, mpangilio wa wastani wa m² 45, na starehe zote za nyumbani. Mahali pazuri kwa familia zinazochunguza Serengeti, Ngorongoro, na Ziwa Manyara.",
    "Kigongoni Gazella exceeded all my expectations. The room was spotless, the staff incredibly warm, and the breakfast was delicious. Perfect location as a base for Lake Manyara and Ngorongoro. Will definitely return!": "Kigongoni Gazella ilizidi matarajio yangu yote. Chumba kilikuwa safi kabisa, wafanyakazi wenye ukarimu mkubwa, na kiamsha kinywa kitamu. Mahali pazuri kama kituo cha Ziwa Manyara na Ngorongoro. Hakika nitarejea!",
    "Fantastic value for money! We used this as our Serengeti safari base and it was perfect. Very comfortable beds, hot shower every morning, and the staff went out of their way to help arrange our game drives. Highly recommend.": "Thamani bora ya pesa! Tulitumia hapa kama kituo chetu cha safari ya Serengeti na ilikuwa kamili. Vitanda vizuri sana, bafu ya maji moto kila asubuhi, na wafanyakazi walijituma kutusaidia kupanga safari za wanyama. Ninapendekeza sana.",
    "Tulikaa na familia yetu kwa wiki moja — vyumba vizuri sana, chakula kitamu na wafanyakazi wema kupita kiasi. Mtoto wangu alisema ni safari yake nzuri zaidi! Tutarudi tena bila shaka.": "Tulikaa na familia yetu kwa wiki moja — vyumba vizuri sana, chakula kitamu na wafanyakazi wema kupita kiasi. Mtoto wangu alisema ni safari yake nzuri zaidi! Tutarudi tena bila shaka.",
    "The best base for a northern Tanzania circuit. Clean, affordable, great food. The staff helped us plan our entire itinerary — Ngorongoro, Serengeti and Lake Manyara — all from right here in Mto wa Mbu. Superb hospitality!": "Kituo bora cha mzunguko wa kaskazini mwa Tanzania. Safi, nafuu, chakula kizuri. Wafanyakazi walitusaidia kupanga safari yetu yote — Ngorongoro, Serengeti na Ziwa Manyara — wote kutoka hapa Mto wa Mbu. Ukarimu mzuri sana!",
    "Such a hidden gem in Mto wa Mbu! Incredibly warm welcome, comfortable family room for all four of us. Loved the evening atmosphere and the local flavors at dinner. The whole team made us feel right at home in Tanzania.": "Ni kito kilichofichika Mto wa Mbu! Mapokezi ya joto sana, chumba cha familia kizuri kwa sisi wote wanne. Tulipenda mazingira ya jioni na ladha za kienyeji kwenye chakula cha jioni. Timu nzima ilitufanya tujisikie kama nyumbani Tanzania.",
